						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 30 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Mahādēva at Tiruchchōṟṟuttuṟai in Kiḻār-kūṟṟam by <hi rend="bold">Muḷḷūr-Naṅgaiyār the mother of Śōḻamahādēvīyār.</hi> The same donor has figured in No. 74 above from Tiruppūndurutti.</p>						

